data.name: LbIntro.Text
data.value: Paste warning lines from your build result ("1> Consider app.config remapping of assembly...") to Input tab and click "Process". Look at Log tab to make sure that there are no errors, and copy the result from Output tab to your App.config or Web.config. Also, it might be worth running in NuGet Package Console redirect update command, "Add-BindingRedirect *" after changes.
